headline: Better Semiconductor Stock: TSMC vs. Nvidia

Artificial intelligence (AI) played a central role in this remarkable surge.  Nvidia (NASDAQ: NVDA) was one of the biggest beneficiaries of this rally, gaining close to 702% in the past two years as companies and governments have been buying its AI chips hand over fist.
